.Dd November 14, 2001
.Dt LABS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm labs
.Nd return the absolute value of a long integer
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libc
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In stdlib.h
.Ft long
.Fn labs "long j"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn labs
function
returns the absolute value of the long integer
.Fa j .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr abs 3 ,
.Xr cabs 3 ,
.Xr floor 3 ,
.Xr imaxabs 3 ,
.Xr llabs 3 ,
.Xr math 3
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Fn labs
function
conforms to
.St -isoC .
.Sh BUGS
The absolute value of the most negative integer remains negative.
